<p>More information about how to add a Usenet indexing service to <?php echo $appname; ?> can be found <a href="http://sickbeard.com/config.html" target="_new">here</a>.</p>
<p><?php echo $appname; ?> does not have official mobile clients, but there are many alternatives for both Android and iOS. <a href="http://nzb360.com/" target="_new">NZB360</a> is one of the best Usenet managers for Android, and <a href="http://nzbunity.dozenzb.com/" target="_new">nzbUnity</a> can be used on jailbroken iOS devices.</p>